Package: media-debuger
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libqt5widgets5
Description: Media file debug and analysis tool (Qt5)
 A Qt5-based application for debugging and analyzing media files,
 providing detailed information about video/audio formats and codecs.

